 up information regarding Khumalo's involvement in the murder and arrested him in the area. They recovered a firearm that was believed to be the murder weapon. Muthwa's initial disappearance sparked an outcry on social media amid ongoing fears of gender-based violence which reached boiling point during the #AmINext movement in mid-2019. News24